(1. INTRODUCTION) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Karnataka Road Development Corporation Ltd \(KRDC\), on behalf of the) Tj T*
(Government of Karnataka, invites e-tenders from Joint Ventures of eligible) Tj T*
(contractors for the following work:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Work Name     : 4-Laning of SH-43 \(Kalaburagi to Bidar\), Package 02,) Tj T*
(                Ch. 48+200 to Ch. 82+800 \(34.6 km\), including pavement) Tj T*
(                strengthening, widening, drainage, structures, and road furniture) Tj T*
(Estimated Cost : Rs. 35,00,00,000/- \(Rs. Thirty-Five Crore\)) Tj T*
(EMD            : Rs. 70,00,000/-) Tj T*
(Performance Security : 5% of contract value) Tj T*
(Completion Period : 30 months) Tj T*
(Defect Liability : 24 months) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Note: For KSHIP-III packages with Estimated Cost above Rs. 20 Crore,) Tj T*
(only Joint Venture bids are accepted per KRDC Procurement Manual 2023,) Tj T*
(Clause 4.7.2.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
