(Publication of NIT              : 10 June 2026) Tj T*
(Last date for submission        : 25 July 2026, 15:00 hrs) Tj T*
(Opening of Technical Bids       : 28 July 2026, 11:00 hrs) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. SCOPE OF WORK) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.1 Pavement Works) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Existing road: single-lane / intermediate lane bituminous road, carriageway) Tj T*
(  3.75 m to 5.5 m, heavily distressed.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Proposed: 4-lane divided carriageway \(2x7.0 m\) with 1.5 m paved shoulders.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Construction sequence:) Tj T*
(  \(a\) Earthwork for widening, including borrow excavation and embankment.) Tj T*
(  \(b\) Granular Sub-Base \(GSB\), Wet Mix Macadam \(WMM\) on widened portion.) Tj T*
(  \(c\) Milling of existing pavement \(50 mm\).) Tj T*
(  \(d\) Bituminous Macadam \(BM\) 75 mm overlay on existing.) Tj T*
(  \(e\) Dense Bituminous Macadam \(DBM\) 50 mm on widened portion.) Tj T*
(  \(f\) Bituminous Concrete \(BC\) 40 mm surface course   full width.) Tj T*
(  \(g\) Central median \(RCC kerb, median cover slab, W-beam crash barrier\).) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.2 Structures) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Three minor bridges \(span 6 m, 6 m, 9 m\)   rehabilitation and widening.) Tj T*
(  Twelve culverts \(RCC box, 900 mm to 1200 mm diameter\)   new construction.) Tj T*
(  Two box drains \(1.2 m   1.2 m\) at township crossings.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.3 Road Furniture) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Signage as per IRC 67:2012, road markings, km posts, delineators,) Tj T*
(  crash barriers \(W-beam\), bus bays \(3 locations\).) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.1 Entity Type \(Mandatory Prerequisite   evaluated before all other criteria\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Standalone bids: NOT ELIGIBLE.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Only Joint Ventures or Consortia will be considered. A JV shall consist) Tj T*
(  of two or more firms. The JV Agreement \(duly stamped and notarised\) must) Tj T*
(  be submitted with the Technical Bid.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  JV Composition Requirements:) Tj T*
(  \(a\) One firm must be designated the Lead Partner, holding not less than) Tj T*
(      51% equity share in the JV.) Tj T*
(  \(b\) Each partner other than the Lead Partner must hold not less than 26%) Tj T*
(      equity share.) Tj T*
