(  \(c\) Maximum three partners in any JV.) Tj T*
(  \(d\) The Lead Partner shall be the single point of contact with KRDC and) Tj T*
(      shall be responsible for all contractual obligations.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Ineligible structures:) Tj T*
(  - Single company bids \(regardless of financial or technical capacity\)) Tj T*
(  - Special Purpose Vehicles \(SPVs\) without minimum 2 JV partners) Tj T*
(  - JVs where lead partner holds less than 51%) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.2 Financial Eligibility \(applicable to JV as a whole unless specified\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Table 1   Financial Criteria) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Sl. | Criterion        | Requirement) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 1  | Combined Turnover | Average Annual Turnover of the JV \(aggregate of) Tj T*
(    |                  | all partners\) not less than Rs. 40.00 Crore per) Tj T*
(    |                  | year from road / highway / civil works, averaged) Tj T*
(    |                  | over the last 3 financial years) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 2  | Lead Partner     | Lead Partner's Average Annual Turnover not less) Tj T*
(    | Turnover         | than Rs. 20.00 Crore per year from road / highway) Tj T*
(    |                  | works, averaged over the last 3 financial years) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 3  | Net Worth        | Combined Net Worth of all JV partners not less) Tj T*
(    |                  | than Rs. 5.00 Crore as on 31 March 2026) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.3 Technical Eligibility) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Table 2   Technical Criteria) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Sl. | Criterion        | Requirement) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 1  | Experience       | Lead Partner OR the JV collectively must have) Tj T*
(    |                  | successfully completed at least 2 similar highway) Tj T*
(    |                  | or road widening works, each of value not less) Tj T*
(    |                  | than Rs. 8.00 Crore, in the last 7 years) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 2  | Certification    | Lead Partner must hold valid ISO 9001:2015) Tj T*
(    |                  | certification \(current\)) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
( 3  | Registration     | Lead Partner must hold valid Karnataka PWD) Tj T*
(    |                  | registration   Class I or above) Tj T*
(----|------------------|--------------------------------------------------) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.4 Documents Required \(to be submitted by Lead Partner on behalf of JV\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  \(a\) Signed and notarised JV Agreement specifying equity shares) Tj T*
(  \(b\) Power of Attorney authorising Lead Partner to act for the JV) Tj T*
(  \(c\) Audited financial statements of each partner \(3 years\)) Tj T*
(  \(d\) Performance certificates for qualifying similar works) Tj T*
(  \(e\) ISO 9001:2015 certificate \(Lead Partner\)) Tj T*
(  \(f\) Karnataka PWD registration certificate \(Lead Partner\)) Tj T*
(  \(g\) GST, PAN, EPF / ESIC of each partner) Tj T*
